name: Rouge the Bat (Found file)
description:
Rouge the Bat from the Sonic series. I found this file on some lora collection a but the download seems to be missing now, so I'm reuploading here. If the original creator would like this file removed, reach out and I'll take it down.

I fond the most success with a weight of 1, but dropping it a bit (0.85-0.95) can help sometimes. Use "bat wings, black bodysuit, white gloves, boots, heart" to get more consistency on the outfit, "elbow gloves" was helpful sometimes too. As with most non-human characters, constancy can be an issue so generate a few images at a time for good results. Highly recommend to use inpaint/photoshop as even the best outputs have some issues.
